  fiber: 11 g
  sodium: 1950 mg
servings: 2
time required: 45 minutes
cuisine: Caribbean
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/cuban-style-sazon-chicken-66c4c40426ca95138237d12e
course: main course
